            The clause simply states,
            <q>the appointment of members by the existing authorities",</q>
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_272gc' title='Col. 272GC &mdash; HL Deb 06 May 2004 vol 660 c272GC' name='column_272gc' href='#column_272gc' rel='bookmark'>272GC</a>
