      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0660P0-05251'>
        <a name='S5LV0660P0_20040506_GCR_281'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-jeff-rooker' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040506_GCR_281' title='Link to this speech by Mr Jeff Rooker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-jeff-rooker" title="Mr Jeff Rooker">Lord Rooker</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
